    "description": "Happy Animal Testing simultaneously puts you in the mindset of a cooperative lab rat, a saboteuring monkey, and a suicidal bunny. Play alone or with your friends as you attempt to navigate a maze of puzzles with ranging levels of difficulty. Work together or prove that you are the most smartest-est of your cohorts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586470/extras/5b749fd1e9285e0b1c43db98ffb2d56e.avif?t=1673892002\" width=531 height=82 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Multiplayer Puzzle-Platformer &gt;𝚃𝙷𝟺𝚃 𝚆𝟷𝙻𝙻 𝚃𝙴𝟻𝚃 𝚃𝙷𝙴 𝙵𝟶𝚄𝙽𝙳𝟺𝚃𝟷𝟶𝙽 𝟶𝙵 𝚈𝟶𝚄𝚁 𝚃𝚁𝚄𝟻𝚃<br></li><li> Casual Level-Roulette &gt;𝚃𝟶 𝙲𝟶𝚁𝚁𝚄𝙿𝚃 𝚈𝟶𝚄𝚁 𝙵𝟺𝟷𝚃𝙷 𝟷𝙽 𝙵𝚁𝟷𝙴𝙽𝙳𝟻𝙷𝟷𝙿𝟻<br></li><li> Quick-Thinking Action-Packed Levels &gt;𝚃𝙷𝟺𝚃 𝚆𝟷𝙻𝙻 𝙿𝚁𝟶𝙱𝟺𝙱𝙻𝚈 𝙳𝙴𝟻𝚃𝚁𝟶𝚈 𝚈𝟶𝚄<br></li><li> Stylistically Simple Graphics &gt;𝚆𝟷𝚃𝙷 𝟺 𝙵𝟶𝙲𝚄𝟻 𝟶𝙽 *𝚉𝚁𝚃* 𝙱𝚁𝚄𝚃𝟺𝙻𝟷𝚃𝚈<br></li><li> A Gigglefest &gt;𝙵𝟶𝚁 𝚃𝙷𝟶𝟻𝙴 𝚆𝙷𝟶 𝚆𝙰𝙽𝚃 𝚃𝟶 𝟻𝙴𝙴 𝚃𝙷𝙴 𝚆𝟶𝚁𝙻𝙳 𝙱𝚄𝚁𝙽<br></li><li> Singleplayer Mode &gt;𝙵𝟶𝚁 𝙷𝚄𝙼𝙰𝙽𝟻 𝚆𝙷𝟶 𝙷𝟺𝚃𝙴 𝙷𝚄𝙼𝙰𝙽𝟻<br></li><li> &gt;𝚁𝙴𝚅𝙴𝙽𝙶𝙴</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586470/extras/21d2e62355d89842d59725bd31564cb9.avif?t=1673892002\" width=531 height=82 /></span>",
